data.description: Welcome to the magnificent Lake Helen property that fulfills all your dreams of a perfect home. This custom-built marvel, with three bedrooms and two bathrooms, boasts the distinction of being a one-owner masterpiece. Designed to accommodate both your beloved animals and your cherished toys, this property offers an abundance of space and functionality. Prepare to be amazed by the extensive range of amenities this property has to offer. The thrill-seekers among you will appreciate the presence of a remarkable 1-mile clay motorcross track, complete with eight jumps, offering an adrenaline-pumping experience right at your doorstep. For those with a passion for shooting sports, a professionally designed shooting range awaits, providing the perfect setting for honing your skills. Additionally, a permanent deer stand has been thoughtfully positioned to provide an elevated viewpoint, allowing for a truly immersive wildlife experience. Seeking relaxation and leisure? Look no further than the immaculately maintained above ground pool, where you can take a refreshing dip on hot summer days. Adjacent to the pool, a well-crafted deck invites you to soak up the sun's warm embrace or entertain guests in a refined outdoor setting. Spanning an expansive 10 acres, this property is not only vast, but also fully devoid of wetlands, allowing for limitless possibilities to be explored. Every inch of this landscaped haven is primed for your enjoyment, ensuring maximum use and convenience. Your four-legged companions will find their own slice of paradise here, with fenced dog runs providing a safe and secure area for them to roam and play freely. Moreover, a dedicated fenced area has been created specifically for your donkeys or horses, guaranteeing their comfort and safety. Aspiring homesteaders will delight in the presence of a well-built chicken coop, ensuring a fresh supply of eggs on a daily basis. Beyond the boundaries of the main residence, an outdoor oasis awaits you. Numerous covered patios are strategically placed throughout the property, providing serene spots to unwind and savor the natural beauty surrounding you. Whether it's reading a book, enjoying a peaceful morning coffee, or hosting memorable gatherings, these outdoor spaces cater to your every need. A covered outdoor kitchen area awaits, allowing for all the grilling experiences of your dreams. In summation, this remarkable Lake Helen property offers a supreme blend of luxury and practicality. With an array of exceptional features, ample space, and a prime location, this property is an exemplary choice for those seeking a tranquil yet adventure-filled lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to claim this extraordinary property as your own, and experience the joy and privilege of residing in your ultimate dream home.
